{
  "uid": "workspace-worker",
  "title": "Workspace Worker",
  "description": "Workspace worker task queue consumer monitoring ",
  "tags": ["automatos", "worker", "tasks"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-1h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "datasource",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": {
          "selected": true,
          "text": "Prometheus",
          "value": "prometheus"
        },
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "multi": false,
        "options": [],
        "refresh": 1,
        "regex": "",
        "skipUrlSync": false
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "title": "Worker Metrics",
      "type": "row",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Dashboard Status",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 1 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Placeholder Dashboard\n\nThis dashboard requires custom Prometheus metrics from the Workspace Worker service on port **8081**.\n\nThe worker consumes tasks from the Redis task queue and processes them. Once the worker exposes a `/metrics` endpoint with `automatos_worker_*` metrics, these panels will populate automatically.\n\n### Planned Metrics\n| Metric | Type | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| `automatos_worker_active_tasks` | Gauge | Currently executing tasks |\n| `automatos_worker_task_duration_seconds` | Histogram | Task processing duration |\n| `automatos_worker_queue_depth` | Gauge | Pending tasks in Redis queue |\n| `automatos_worker_task_total` | Counter | Total tasks processed (by status) |\n| `automatos_worker_errors_total` | Counter | Total task processing errors |",
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false }
      }
    },
    {
      "title": "Task Processing",
      "type": "row",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "id": 3,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Active Tasks",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 7 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 5 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 10 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "noValue": "Awaiting backend deploy",
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "automatos_worker_active_tasks",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "instant": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Queue Depth",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 7 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 50 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 200 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "noValue": "Awaiting backend deploy",
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "automatos_worker_queue_depth",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "instant": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Avg Task Duration",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 7 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 30 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 120 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "s",
          "noValue": "Awaiting backend deploy",
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rate(automatos_worker_task_duration_seconds_sum[5m]) / rate(automatos_worker_task_duration_seconds_count[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "instant": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Error Rate",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 7 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 0.01 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.05 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "noValue": "Awaiting backend deploy",
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rate(automatos_worker_errors_total[5m]) / rate(automatos_worker_task_total[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "instant": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Trends ",
      "type": "row",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 13 },
      "id": 8,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "title": "Task Throughput",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 14 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": { "legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "off" }
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "ops",
          "noValue": "Awaiting backend deploy",
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rate(automatos_worker_task_total{status=\"success\"}[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "Success/s"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "rate(automatos_worker_task_total{status=\"failure\"}[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "Failure/s"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "title": "Queue Depth Over Time",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 14 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 30,
            "gradientMode": "scheme",
            "hideFrom": { "legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "line" }
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 200 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "noValue": "Awaiting backend deploy",
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "automatos_worker_queue_depth",
          "legendFormat": "Queue Depth"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}